item.title: I am looking for Haiti data
item.dc:creator: amys
item.description:
Hi, have you had a look at the site d-portal?

You can select the country Haiti, and type in ‘school’ or ‘hospital’ and do a search and see what comes up.

Any further questions, do e-mail me at support@iatistandard.org
